---
import Modal from "./Modal.astro";
---

<Modal id='help-modal' title='about bunbu'>
    <div class='faq-section'>
        <div class='chat-container'>
            <div class='chat-message question'>
                <p>what is bunbu?</p>
            </div>
            <div class='chat-message answer'>
                <p>
                    bunbu is a web application that performs frequency analysis on
                    japanese text. it breaks down the text into individual words in
                    their dictionary form, and provides statistics on their usage.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class='chat-message question'>
                <p>what is the "dictionary form" of a word?</p>
            </div>
            <div class='chat-message answer'>
                <p>
                    the dictionary form is the basic version of a word; the way you'd
                    find it in a dictionary. for example, the verb「食べる」(to eat) is
                    the dictionary form of「食べた」(ate),「食べている」(eating), etc.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class='chat-message question'>
                <p>what inspired bunbu?</p>
            </div>
            <div class='chat-message answer'>
                <p>
                    bunbu was inspired by <a
                        href='https://osc.garden/blog/ichiko-aoba-lyrics-japanese-morphology/'
                        >this article</a
                    > on analysing japanese song lyrics to learn japanese.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class='chat-message question'>
                <p>how is my privacy protected when using bunbu?</p>
            </div>
            <div class='chat-message answer'>
                <p>your data never leaves your device:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>local processing:</strong> all text analysis is performed
                        on your device
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>no data collection:</strong> neither your text nor the analysis
                        results are sent to any server
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>no ai:</strong> your text is not used to train any machine
                        learning models
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>no cookies:</strong> this site doesn't use cookies or any
                        other tracking technologies
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>open source:</strong> the code is open source and available
                        for inspection <a href='https://github.com/welpo/bunbu'
                            >on github</a
                        >
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Modal>

<style>
    .chat-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-md);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: var(--space-md);
    }

    .chat-message {
        box-shadow:
            rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 3px 0px,
            rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06) 0px 1px 2px 0px;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        padding: 12px;
        max-width: 80%;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .chat-message p {
        margin: 0;
    }

    .chat-message.question {
        align-self: flex-end;
        background-color: #dcf8c6;
        color: #000;
    }

    .chat-message.answer {
        align-self: flex-start;
        background-color: #fff;
        color: #000;
    }

    .chat-message.answer ul {
        margin: 8px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .chat-message.answer li {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .chat-message a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
</style>
